                "category": "offensive",
                "description": {
                    "value": "<p>Bronco lurches its entire body, spewing forth chunks of meteorite in a @Template[cone|distance:30] that deal @Damage[5d6[bludgeoning]|options:area-damage] damage to all creatures in the area (@Check[reflex|dc:25|basic|options:area-effect]). The area becomes difficult terrain for 1 minute, though a creature can use an Interact action to clear one square of the rubble. Bronco can't Vomit Meteorites for [[/gmr 1d4 #Recharge Vomit Meteorites]]{1d4 rounds}.</p>"
